data.description: Completion Scheduled for End of February 2021! The Redbud by H&H Homes is a two-story home featuring 5 bedrooms,  3 baths, and a 2-car garage. The main floor provides ample space for entertaining, consisting of a family room with fireplace, formal dining room, spacious kitchen with a 9 ft. eat-at-island, casual dining area, walk-in pantry, & butler's pantry.  A bedroom and bath complete the lower level - perfect for guests! The second level houses the owner's suite, as well as an additional 3 bedrooms, bathroom, loft & laundry room. The front porch area is covered and the covered back patio provides extra space to entertain.
